						               													<description>This is a Japanese science fiction wargame set in the universe of the Legend of the Galactic Heroes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Seven scenarios are contained in the game, and the fictional space battle that each was drawn in the story is reproduced. These are being called a fleet battle, but when either is said, it is close to the land battle of Napoleonic age.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player control one or more star fleets. &amp;#10;Each fleet is commanded by one admiral, and organized by 10 to 20 ships units.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each turn, a fleet are activated in the unintentional order by chit-pull system, and it resolves a movement and a combat. &amp;#10;An average admiral has only one or two chits. But the heroes of the story has four or more chits, and it is activated  many times during one turn. &amp;#10;A battle is resolved with adjacent hex on the Odds CRT.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The outcome is decided by the number which made a fleet collapse. A fleet collapses when a fixed unit is eliminate or admiral's mental agitation.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
